title: AIESEC
description: AIESEC's brand colors are vibrant and dynamic, reflecting their commitment to inspiring and empowering young leaders globally. The palette includes energetic shades like blue (#037EF3), orange (#F85A40), green (#00C16E), and purple (#7552CC), among others. These colors are taken from AIESEC's official brand guidelines, emphasizing the diversity and dynamism at the core of their identity.
